#DisneyKids: Last Chance To Enter To Win a Dream Vacation to Walt Disney World Resort 
by Michelle Baumann , Walt Disney World Public Relations 
Is your preschooler dreaming of a trip to Walt Disney World Resort ? We all know that a child’s first visit to a Disney theme park is magical. It’s pure wonder and awe. That’s why Disney Junior wants to send your family on an unforgettable vacation to Walt Disney World Resort! From first safaris and first waterpark splashes to Star Wars adventures or seeing their favorite Disney Junior pals come to life, Disney firsts provide unforgettable memories. 
From now through February 26 you can enter the Disney Junior, “My Magical First Sweepstakes,” to win a truly magical family vacation to Walt Disney World Resort – just visit the sweepstakes website for all of the details . Good luck, and happy planning! 
NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. Void where prohibited. Open only to legal residents of the 50 U.S. or D.C who are 18 years of age or older (or who have reached the age of majority in his/her primary state of residence, whichever is older). Sweepstakes starts 12:00pm (noon) PT on 1/30/17 and ends 11:59pm PT on 2/26/17. Click here for Official Rules including details on odds of winning, prize descriptions and limitations.
